show.description: A mother’s love, a husband’s betrayal, and a friend’s darkest secret! The Perfect Revenge is a storm of revenge, deceit, and shattered relationships that will keep you on the edge of your seat. Will truth win over lies, or will greed destroy it all? Watch now.
